-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_returns.sql
```sql
-- Deduplicate returns to one approved return per item
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        item_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY return_date ASC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    item_id,
    return_date,
    reason,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

-- models/intermediate/int_product_returns.sql
```sql
-- Calculate total items returned per product
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        oi.product_id,
        COUNT(dr.item_id) AS total_items_returned
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} dr
        ON dr.item_id = oi.item_id
    GROUP BY oi.product_id
)
SELECT
    product_id,
    total_items_returned
FROM source
```

-- Join products to categories with category_id handling
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        p.product_id,
        COALESCE(c.category_id, -1) AS category_id,
        COALESCE(c.name, '(unknown)') AS category_name
    FROM {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_categories') }} c
        ON c.category_id = p.category_id
)

    category_id,
    category_name
FROM source

-- models/mart/fct_return_rates_by_category.sql
```sql
-- Calculate return rates by category
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        cp.category_name,
        COALESCE(ps.total_items_sold, 0) AS total_items_sold,
        COALESCE(pr.total_items_returned, 0) AS total_items_returned,
        CASE
            WHEN COALESCE(ps.total_items_sold, 0) > 0
            THEN COALESCE(pr.total_items_returned, 0)::DECIMAL / COALESCE(ps.total_items_sold, 0)
            ELSE 0
        END AS return_rate
    FROM {{ ref('int_category_products') }} cp
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_product_sales') }} ps
        ON ps.product_id = cp.product_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_product_returns') }} pr
        ON pr.product_id = cp.product_id
)
SELECT
    category_name,
    SUM(total_items_sold) AS total_items_sold,
    SUM(total_items_returned) AS total_items_returned,
    SUM(total_items_returned)::DECIMAL / NULLIF(SUM(total_items_sold), 0) AS return_rate
FROM source
GROUP BY category_name
ORDER BY return_rate DESC
